<h2 id="individual-differences">Individual Differences</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Long term
    <ul>
      <li>sex, physical and intellectual abilities</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Short term
    <ul>
      <li>effect of stress or fatigue(í”¼ë¡œë„; ì§€ì†ì ì¸)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Changing
    <ul>
